{"word":"H7153 - קִרְיַת אַרְבַּע - Qiryath ʼArbaʻ - keer-yath' ar-bah' - Kirjath-arba","slug":"H7153","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קִרְיַת אַרְבַּע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Qiryath ʼArbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keer-yath' ar-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Kirjath-arba"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>קרית הארבּע קרית ארבּע</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>qiryath 'arba‛ qiryath hâ'arba‛</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>keer-yath' ar-bah'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Kirjath-arba = \"city of Arba\" <ol><li>early name of the city which after the conquest was called 'Hebron'</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a> and <a href=\"#/H704\">H704</a> or <a href=\"#/H702\">H702</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4745\">H4745</a>, <a href=\"#/H4746\">H4746</a>, <a href=\"#/H6982\">H6982</a>, <a href=\"#/H704\">H704</a>, <a href=\"#/H7136\">H7136</a>, <a href=\"#/H7137\">H7137</a>, <a href=\"#/H7147\">H7147</a>, <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a>, <a href=\"#/H7152\">H7152</a>, <a href=\"#/H7154\">H7154</a>, <a href=\"#/H7155\">H7155</a>, <a href=\"#/H7156\">H7156</a>, <a href=\"#/H7157\">H7157</a>, <a href=\"#/H7158\">H7158</a>, <a href=\"#/H7176\">H7176</a>, <a href=\"#/H7177\">H7177</a>, <a href=\"#/H7178\">H7178</a>"}]}